nd%20its%20allies%20and%20partners'%20larger%20exercise%20on%20testing%20weapons%20and%20training%20together.%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%20photo%20by%20Mass%20Communication%20Specialist%20Seaman%20Anthony%20Vilardi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20Japanese%20torpedo%20sank%20a%20decommissioned%20US%20Navy%20vessel%20as%20part%20of%20a%20live-fire%20drill.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20USS%20Juneau%20was%20an%20amphibious%20transport%20dock%20ship%20that%20saw%20action%20in%20the%20Vietnam%20War%20and%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20first%20USS%20Juneau%20was%20sunk%20by%20an%20enemy%20Japanese%20torpedo%20in%20World%20War%20II.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOver%2080%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20Japanese%20submarine%20attacked%20and%20sank%20the%20US%20Navy%20ship%20USS%20Juneau.%20Now%2C%20a%20Japanese%20torpedo%20sent%20another%20American%20vessel%20bearing%20that%20same%20name%20to%20the%20ocean%20floor%2C%20but%20under%20very%20different%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20recent%20exercise%2C%20the%20US%20and%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-army-looking-to-drone-boats-help-pacific-watercraft-problems-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPacific%20allies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20partners%20conducted%20a%20live-fire%20sinking%20of%20the%20decommissioned%20Austin-class%20amphibious%20transport%20dock%20USS%20Juneau.%20The%20Navy%20said%20that%20the%20live-fire%20sinking%20was%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20effort%20to%20practice%20coordinated%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewarfighting%20with%20American%20allies%20and%20partners%20across%20air%2C%20sea%2C%20land%2C%20space%2C%20and%20cyber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20live-fire%20event%2C%20called%20a%20SINKEX%2C%20was%20part%20of%20Valiant%20Shield%202026%2C%20a%20large-scale%20exercise%20that%20brought%20the%20US%2C%20Japan%2C%20Australia%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20New%20Zealand%20together%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-and-japan-struck-deal-to-make-more-patriot-missiles-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etest%20weapons%20and%20train%3C%2Fa%3E%20together%20in%20a%20more%20realistic%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Japan%20Maritime%20Self-Defense%20Force%20submarine%20struck%20the%20decommissioned%20USS%20Juneau%20with%20a%20torpedo.%20Before%20the%20exercise%2C%20crews%20removed%20hazardous%20materials%20and%20pollutants%20from%20the%20ship.%20Officials%20also%20surveyed%20the%20sinking%20site%2C%20which%20was%20more%20than%20200%20nautical%20miles%20offshore%20in%20the%20Mariana%20Islands%20Range%20Complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUSS%20Juneau%20(LPD-10)%20entered%20service%20in%201969%20and%20participated%20in%20the%20Vietnam%20War%20and%20operations%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20transporting%20troops%20into%20combat.%20The%20Navy%20decommissioned%20the%20ship%20in%202008.%20Named%20after%20the%20capital%20of%20Alaska%2C%20the%20vessel%20was%20an%20amphibious%20warfare%20ship%20designed%20to%20move%20forces%20to%20land%20in%20conflicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225352%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20large%2C%20decommissioned%20US%20Navy%20vessel%20starts%20to%20sink%20in%20dark%20blue%20ocean%20waters.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4555b0ec11c5f7e7fa7275%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223011%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20USS%20Juneau%20was%20an%20amphibious%20transport%20dock%20ship%20that%20saw%20action%20in%20the%20Vietnam%20War%20and%20Operation%20Desert%20Storm.%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%20photo%20by%20Mass%20Communication%20Specialist%20Seaman%20Anthony%20Vilardi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20amphibious%20transport%20vessel%20was%20the%20third%20US%20Navy%20ship%20to%20be%20named%20Juneau.%20The%20second%20was%20a%20Juneau-class%20light%20cruiser%20commissioned%20in%201946%20and%20active%20in%20the%20Korean%20War.%20The%20first%20USS%20Juneau%20was%20an%20Atlanta-class%20light%20cruiser.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUSS%20Juneau%20(CL-52)%20was%20commissioned%20in%201942%20and%20fought%20in%20some%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-troops-surveys-about-japan-war-after-pearl-harbor-attack-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EWorld%20War%20II%3C%2Fa%3E's%20deadliest%20naval%20battles.%20During%20the%20Guadalcanal%20campaign%20in%20November%201942%2C%20a%20torpedo%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnavies-lost-interest-in-cruiser-submarines-during-wwii-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJapanese%20submarine%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnavies-lost-interest-in-cruiser-submarines-during-wwii-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI-26%20%3C%2Fa%3Estruck%20the%20Juneau%20and%20sank%20it.%20The%20ship%20had%20previously%20been%20crippled%20by%20a%20torpedo%20fired%20from%20the%20Japanese%20destroyer%20Amatsukaze.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22USS%20Juneau%20(CL-52)%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4560efec11c5f7e7fa731c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221036%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUSS%20Juneau%20(CL-52).%3Cp%3EBureau%20of%20Ships%20Collection%20in%20the%20US%20National%20Archives%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%20687%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20action%2C%20including%20five%20brothers%20from%20Iowa%20who%20became%20symbols%20of%20wartime%20sacrifice%20after%20their%20ship%20was%20lost%20in%20combat.%20Only%2010%20crew%20members%20survived%20the%20attack.%20A%20research%20crew%20discovered%20the%20wreck%20of%20USS%20Juneau%20in%20March%202018%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20the%20Solomon%20Islands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20live-fire%20exercise%20bore%20certain%20echoes%20of%20history%20but%20also%20served%20as%20a%20reminder%20of%20how%20far%20US-Japanese%20relations%20have%20come%20over%20the%20past%20eight%20decades%20since%20the%20end%20of%20World%20War%20II.%20Emerging%20threats%20in%20the%20Pacific%20region%20have%20only%20strengthened%20those%20ties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20SINKEX%20provided%20an%20outstanding%20opportunity%20for%20our%20joint%20team%20to%20integrate%20capabilities%20across%20domains%2C%20honing%20the%20lethal%20precision%20and%20coordination%20essential%20for%20high-end%20maritime%20operations%20in%20the%20Pacific%20theater%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rear%20Adm.%20Eric%20Anduze%2C%20commander%20of%20Carrier%20Strike%20Group%205%20and%20Task%20Force%2070%2C%20in%20a%20press%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELive-fire%20strikes%20on%20real%2C%20decommissioned%20vessels%20are%20a%20regular%20part%20of%20naval%20training%20and%20give%20troops%20a%20realistic%20understanding%20of%20how%20systems%20work%20on%20actual%20targets%20compared%20to%20simulated%20environments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapanese-torpedo-sinks-us-navy-decommissioned-vessel-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782987421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a45577e1aaffe3020cb1685%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapanese-torpedo-sinks-us-navy-decommissioned-vessel-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20first%20USS%20Juneau%20was%20a%20light%20cruiser%20that%20was%20struck%20and%20sunk%20by%20a%20Japanese%20torpedo%20in%201942%2C%20killing%20all%20but%2010%20of%20the%20vessel's%20crew.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cpanella%40businessinsider.com%20(Chris%20Panella)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adar%20Poonawalla%20Family%20Office%20invests%20%E2%82%B9700%20crore%20in%20Inox%20Clean%20Energy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782987207000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2026-01%2F07%2Fthumb%2Ffit