%26quot%3B%20isn't%20as%20important%20as%20being%20able%20to%20learn%20quickly%2C%20Anne%20Tse%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpepsi-apac-ceo-prioritizes-curiosity-in-ai-era-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAPAC%20CEO%20of%20PepsiCo%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20She%20said%20that%20the%20company%20prioritizes%20curiosity%20in%20all%20candidates%2C%20but%20especially%20in%20junior%20hires.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20all%20about%20the%20aptitude%2C%20the%20speed%2C%20the%20agility%20to%20learn%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tse%2C%20who%20oversees%20PepsiCo's%20businesses%20across%20Asia%20Pacific%2C%20Australia%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20and%20Greater%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20AI%20era%2C%20she%20said%20workers%20need%20to%20be%20flexible%20as%20technology%20evolves%20and%20the%20company%20responds%20to%20rapidly%20evolving%20consumer%20demands.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20people%20are%20curious%2C%20they%20want%20to%20learn.%20When%20they're%20curious%2C%20they%20also%20are%20willing%20to%20unlearn%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEO%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22279e6fa4-40c7-484c-a188-2c3a7015f767%5C%22%3EStrong%20judgment%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBrian%20Myerholtz%2C%20global%20head%20of%20talent%20acquisition%20at%20Boston%20Consulting%20Group%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20top%20skill%20the%20firm%20looks%20for%20continues%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20judgment%20and%20problem%20solving.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20he%20said%2C%20AI%20has%20raised%20the%20bar%20for%20what%20that%20entails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20no%20longer%20enough%20to%20get%20to%20an%20answer%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20Myerholtz%20told%20Business%20Insider%20via%20email.%20%26quot%3BThe%20best%20talent%20can%20use%20AI%20to%20explore%20more%20possibilities%2C%20pressure-test%20ideas%2C%20and%20then%20apply%20human%20judgment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMyerholtz's%20comments%20come%20as%20the%20firm%20has%20increasingly%20relied%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frip-cover-letters-generative-ai-hiring-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eassessments%20during%20the%20hiring%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20online%20cases%2C%20behavioral%20assessments%2C%20or%20personality%20tests%2C%20to%20narrow%20the%20pool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20can%20accelerate%20the%20process%2C%20but%20people%20still%20create%20the%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20Myerholtz%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275fa1f82-65cd-4104-808d-ca901c3aa4a5%5C%22%3EAdaptability%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFrancesca%20Jones%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fey-early-career-leader-shares-smartest-move-by-candidate-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEY%20US%20early%20careers%20leader%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cu%3E%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%20said%20that%20in%20the%20past%2C%20grades%20may%20have%20been%20the%20No.%201%20attribute%20that%20hiring%20teams%20looked%20for.%20That's%20no%20longer%20the%20case%2C%20she%20said.%20Instead%2C%20they're%20looking%20for%20adaptable%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20what%20we're%20working%20on%20right%20now%20is%20uncertainty%2C%20and%20so%20we%20need%20people%20who%20are%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20navigate%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Jones%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20expecting%20candidates%20to%20explain%20how%20a%20failure%20or%20weakness%20ultimately%20became%20a%20strength%2C%20she%20said%20the%20focus%20is%20now%20on%20how%20they're%20actively%20working%20through%20that%20weakness%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKathy%20Diaz%2C%20Cognizant's%20chief%20people%20officer%2C%20similarly%20said%20that%20the%20firm%20is%20looking%20for%20adaptability%20in%20entry-level%20talent%2C%20and%20that%20the%20trait%20encompasses%20a%20lot%20of%20capabilities%2C%20like%20an%20ability%20to%20learn%20and%20think%20critically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThings%20are%20changing%2C%26quot%3B%20Diaz%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo