ook%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinancial%20Freedom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fearning-more-money-through-side-hustles-to-achieve-financial-freedom-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrew%20his%20net%20worth%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20practically%20nothing%20to%20more%20than%20%241%20million%20in%20five%20years%2C%20has%20watched%20the%20financial%20independence%2C%20retire%20early%20(FIRE)%20movement%20evolve%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20and%20a%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20how%20he%20would%20define%20FIRE%20in%202026%2C%20Sabatier%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20never%20been%20easier%20to%20do%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20may%20sound%20counterintuitive.%20Sabatier%20acknowledged%20that%20parts%20of%20the%20FIRE%20path%20are%20harder%20today%20than%20they%20were%20when%20he%20began.%20Housing%20costs%20are%20higher%2C%20inflation%20has%20squeezed%20budgets%2C%20and%20young%20investors%20no%20longer%20have%20the%20same%20post-2008%20bull-market%20tailwinds%20of%20near%20zero%20interest%20rates%20that%20he%20benefited%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20he%20said%2C%20FIRE%20has%20become%20broader%2C%20more%20flexible%2C%20and%20more%20accessible.%20Plus%2C%20the%20internet%20has%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20start%20businesses%20and%20build%20income%20streams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20FIRE%20is%20attainable%20for%20everyone.%20Literally%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20Sabatier%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20just%20depends.%20The%20timeline%20becomes%20different%2C%20and%20the%20tradeoffs%20become%20different%2C%20and%20they're%20largely%20personal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f823ecb2-f030-4d37-bbb7-528b63e10727%5C%22%3EThe%20internet%20has%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20build%20income%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20early%20FIRE%20movement%20focused%20heavily%20on%20living%20with%20less%2C%20Sabatier%20said%20it%20has%20evolved%20as%20internet-era%20entrepreneurs%20have%20used%20side%20hustles%2C%20online%20businesses%2C%20and%20multiple%20income%20streams%20to%20accelerate%20their%20path%20to%20financial%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFIRE%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-independence-retire-early-fire-coast-debate-personal-finance-investing-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eno%20longer%20only%20about%20spending%20as%20little%20as%20possible%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20many%20people%20pursuing%20it%2C%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20widen%20the%20gap%20between%20income%20and%20expenses%2C%20and%20earning%20more%20can%20be%20just%20as%20important%20as%20cutting%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20okay%2C%20we%20can%20rapidly%20accelerate%20this%20on%20our%20own%20terms%2C%20just%20by%20creating%20different%20types%20of%20businesses%20and%20side%20hustling%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20that%20became%20the%20evolution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Sabatier%2C%20it%20has%20never%20been%20easier%20to%20make%20money%20outside%20a%20traditional%20job.%20The%20internet%20has%20lowered%20the%20barrier%20to%20starting%20a%20business%2C%20reaching%20customers%2C%20and%20building%20an%20audience%20through%20social%20media%2C%20websites%2C%20newsletters%2C%20and%20other%20digital%20tools.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20does%20not%20mean%20every%20side%20hustle%20will%20work%2C%20he%20said%2C%20and%20it%20also%20means%20there%20is%20more%20competition%2C%20but%20the%20opportunity%20set%20is%20much%20larger%20than%20it%20once%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20people%20who%20don't%20know%20where%20to%20start%2C%20Sabatier%20recommends%20making%20two%20lists%3A%20one%20of%20things%20they%20enjoy%20doing%20and%20another%20of%20things%20they%20are%20good%20at.%20The%20overlap%20can%20point%20to%20income%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomeone%20who%20has%20played%20music%20for%20years%20might%20give%20lessons%20or%20play%20gigs%2C%20while%20someone%20who%20loves%20travel%20might%20help%20people%20plan%20trips.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20monetize%20skills%20or%20interests%20that%20already%20come%20naturally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22468e8027-53fa-4418-be5e-00cda57928a3%5C%22%3EFIRE%20has%20become%20a%20'choose%20your%20own%20adventure'%20strategy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESabatier%20said%20FIRE%20has%20also%20become%20easier%20to%20personalize.%20The%20movement%20now%20includes%20offshoots%20such%20as%20Coast%20FIRE%2C%20Barista%20FIRE%2C%20Lean%20FIRE%2C%20and%20Fat%20FIRE.%20Some%20people%20still%20pursue%20traditional%20FIRE%2C%20which%20often%20involves%20saving%20aggressively%20to%20retire%20decades%20early.%20Others%20use%20FIRE%20principles%20to%20work%20less%2C%20change%20careers%2C%20or%20become%20less%20dependent%20on%20a%20paycheck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESabatier%20described%20modern%20FIRE%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bchoose%20your%20own%20adventure%26quot%3B%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone's%20life%20is%20different%2C%20and%20everyone%20has%20different%20opportunities%2C%20and%20everyone%20has%20different%20visions%20for%20their%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20just%20choose%20what%20it%20means%20to%20you%20and%20then%20discard%20the%20rest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESabatier%20is%20still%20clear-eyed%20about%20the%20challenges.%20He%20said%20FIRE%20is%20harder%20for%20lower%20earners%2C%20especially%20as%20inflation%20and%20housing%20costs%20have%20risen.%20While%20he%20believes%20financial%20independence%20is%20possible%20for%20everyone%20in%20some%20form%2C%20the%20timeline%20can%20vary%20widely%20depending%20on%20income%2C%20expenses%2C%20family%20obligations%2C%20and%20geography.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20feel%20like%20it's%20getting%20more%20difficult%20to%20do%20if%20you%20just%20are%20making%20minimum%20wage%20and%20trying%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20housing%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BInflation%20has%20been%20significantly%20higher%20than%20I%20could%20have%20anticipated%2C%20and%20that%20disproportionately%20impacts%20people%20who%20make%20less%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20people%20who%20want%20to%20accelerate%20the%20process%2C%20he%20said%2C%20increasing%20income%20is%20often%20necessary.%20The%20math%20still%20comes%20down%20to%20the%20gap%20between%20income%20and%20expenses%20%E2%80%94%20but%20there%20have%20never%20been%20more%20ways%20to%20widen%20that%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-independence-fire-millennial-investing-multiple-income-streams-side-hustles-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782984901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3ec1e8a25092c74cc9ff4e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-independence-fire-millennial-investing-multiple-income-streams-side-hustles-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20think%20FIRE%20is%20attainable%20for%20everyone.%20Literally%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Grant%20Sabatier.%20Here's%20how%20he%20made%20it%20work.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kelkins%40businessinsider.com%20(Kathleen%20Elkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dulquer%20Salmaan%20to%20be%20summoned%20again%20by%20customs%20in%20luxury%20car%20case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782984813000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132134976%2Cimgsize-124696.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fmalayalam%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fafter-seven-hours-of-investigation-dulquer-salmaan-to-be-summoned-again-by-customs-in-luxury-car-smuggling-case%2Farticleshow%2F132134946.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%