nts%20at%20IDX%20Advisors%20are%20increasingly%20worried%20about%20what%20could%20happen%20to%20their%20portfolios%20if%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-bubble-ai-valuations-nvidia-broadcom-dot-com-crash-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebiggest%20spenders%20in%20the%20AI%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%20suddenly%20decide%20to%20close%20their%20wallets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20reasonable%20fear.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-capex-boom-meta-microsoft-amazon-alphabet-goldman-sachs-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpending%20from%20so-called%20hyperscalers%20like%20Amazon%2C%20Alphabet%2C%20and%20Microsoft%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20infrastructure%20like%20data%20centers%20has%20been%20a%20pillar%20of%20the%20AI%20trade%20that's%20fueled%20the%20gains%20in%20the%20broader%20market.%20If%20investors%20start%20getting%20impatient%20waiting%20for%20spending%20to%20pay%20off%2C%20these%20firms%20could%20tighten%20their%20purse%20strings%20and%20suddenly%20siphon%20off%20the%20massive%20flow%20of%20profits%20for%20capex%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20solid%20signal%20that%20this%20will%20happen%20anytime%20soon%2C%20with%20the%20top%20hyperscalers%20estimated%20to%20spend%20%24920%20billion%20in%202027%2C%20up%20from%20around%20%24750%20billion%20this%20year.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20things%20can%20change%20quickly%20in%20markets%2C%20and%20given%20the%20worries%2C%20McMillan's%20clients%20asked%20him%20to%20screen%20for%20non-semiconductor%20stocks%20that%20could%20give%20them%20the%20best%20of%20both%20worlds.%20That%20is%2C%20companies%20that%20offer%20continued%20exposure%20to%20the%20AI%20trade%20in%20a%20non-pure-play%20way%2C%20while%20also%20not%20being%20over-reliant%20on%20the%20steady%20stream%20of%20hyperscaler%20capex.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody's%20kind%20of%20taking%20profits%20in%20the%20chip%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20McMillan%2C%20IDX%20Advisor's%20chief%20inve