0the%20company%20can't%20meet%20your%20boundaries%2C%20you'll%20find%20one%20that%20can.%20You%20have%20to%20realize%20your%20value%20and%20worth%20before%20you%20even%20put%20your%20foot%20out%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20every%20company%20just%20wants%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-grad-cant-find-job-moving-in-with-parents-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehire%20a%20new%20graduate%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Companies%20want%20someone%20who%20can%20problem-solve%2C%20use%20their%20life%20and%20work%20experiences%20to%20navigate%20different%20situations%2C%20and%20bring%20a%20fresh%20perspective.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fa1b7763-12c3-4a02-b611-9a496d629866%5C%22%3EI%20feel%20like%20I'm%20in%20my%2030s%20again%3B%20it's%20rejuvenating%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wish%20I%20could%20describe%20the%20weight%20lifted%20off%20my%20shoulders%20when%20I%20gave%20notice%20at%20my%20old%20job.%20It%20felt%20like%20I%20went%20from%20suffocating%20to%20finally%20being%20able%20to%20breathe%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20my%20last%20job%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20my%20clients%20could%20tell%20that%20I%20was%20under%20a%20lot%20of%20strain%20or%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20not%20at%20my%20best%2C%20and%20that%20affected%20business.%20At%20my%20new%20job%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20I'm%20attracting%20better%20clients%20and%20business%20because%20I%20like%20who%20I%20am%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20rejuvenated%2C%20like%20I%20did%20in%20my%2020s%20and%2030s.%20It's%20this%20confidence%20that%20once%20a%20client%20meets%20me%2C%20they're%20going%20to%20want%20to%20buy%20from%20me.%20It's%20euphoric%20to%20feel%20like%20I%20can%20breathe%20and%20be%20myself%2C%20supported%20by%20such%20a%20great%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222482%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nicole%20Cicero%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3d5055360acd489560b4dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223108%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECicero%20says%20starting%20over%20in%20her%2050s%20required%20confidence.%3Cp%3EElianel%20Clinton%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220424c488-cce8-4b19-be9f-d00e2365990d%5C%22%3EThat%20being%20said%2C%20this%20transition%20hasn't%20been%20easy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20on%20a%20commission%20plan%2C%20but%20I%20have%20no%20commissions%20at%20this%20moment%2C%20being%20new%20and%20currently%20working%20on%20bringing%20in%20new%20customers.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI'm%20stressed%20out%20trying%20to%20build%20up%20a%20new%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20I%20had%20a%20client%20fall%20through%2C%20and%20it%20threw%20me%20for%20a%20loop.%20I%20have%20to%20remind%20myself%20that%20I%20did%20all%20I%20could%2C%20and%20all%20I%20can%20do%20is%20try%20to%20reel%20them%20back%20in.%20Business%20might%20be%20slow%20right%20now%20as%20I%20go%20through%20growing%20pains%2C%20but%20I'll%20get%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22332c0c87-43b6-4886-adc2-0e15eee83556%5C%22%3EThe%20biggest%20emotional%20challenge%20is%20identity%20loss%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20somebody%20big%20at%20my%20company%20for%2014%20years.%20I%20had%20a%20title%2C%20reputation%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphrases-you-can-use-to-earn-trust-2014-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eclients%20who%20trusted%20me%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20who%20became%20friends.%20Then%20overnight%2C%20nobody%20is%20calling%2C%20and%20nobody%20needs%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20from%20being%20the%20person%20with%20the%20answers%20to%20someone%20starting%20from%20scratch.%20Now%2C%20at%2054%2C%20it%20hits%20differently%20because%20there's%20a%20voice%20inside%20my%20head%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20too%20old%20for%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20I%20needed%20to%20leave%20my%20old%20job%20for%20my%20sanity%20and%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENobody%20warns%20you%20that%20starting%20over%20at%2053%20doesn't%20just%20empty%20your%20bank%20account%3B%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F50-unemployed-worried-hiring-managers-see-desperation-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emesses%20with%20your%20mind%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20I%20still%20keep%20pushing%20forward%2C%20staying%20positive%20and%20manifesting%20success.%20For%20example%2C%20instead%20of%20saying%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20afford%20it%26quot%3B%20anymore%2C%20I'll%20buy%20something%20anyway%20to%20manifest%20the%20fact%20that%20income%20will%20be%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f31536d4-5b17-4001-8367-81d0f90478ac%5C%22%3EIt's%20not%20selfish%20to%20make%20a%20change%20for%20yourself.%20I'm%20setting%20a%20good%20example%20for%20my%20kids.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nicole%20Cicero%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3d5175e218c3b62535d189%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222434%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECicero%20believes%20this%20change%20has%20made%20her%20a%20better%20person.%3Cp%3EElianel%20Clinton%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20reasons%20I%20think%20people%20in%20their%2050s%20stay%20in%20careers%20they're%20unhappy%20with%20is%20because%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20start%20over%20again.%20My%20advice%20is%20to%20believe%20in%20yourself%20and%20take%20the%20first%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20never%20too%20late%20to%20change.%20It's%20not%20selfish.%20In%20fact%2C%20change%20can%20make%20you%20a%20better%20person%20for%20your%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESure%2C%20I%20have%20to%20tell%20my%20kids%20we%20can't%20DoorDash%20as%20much%20food%20as%20we%20used%20to%20because%20I%20started%20over%2C%20but%20they're%20seeing%20me%20get%20up%20every%20morning%2C%20change%20out%20of%20my%20sweatpants%2C%20and%20work%20to%20handle%20this%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hope%20that%20I'm%20setting%20a%20good%20example%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20navigating%20a%20career%20