C%20and%20reusable.%20They%20will%20answer%20the%20hard%20and%20interesting%20data%20questions%20about%20Ads.%20Data%20science%20owns%20the%20models%20and%20algorithms%20that%20power%20our%20products.%20Data%20partners%20closely%20with%20Engineering%20and%20is%20a%20key%20partner%20across%20Product%20Management.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ca5bed15-8c67-4519-9530-f549d8a83b67%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdvertising%20Solutions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3ELed%20by%20%3Cstrong%3EDayna%20Wasilefski%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20VP%2C%20Advertising%20Solutions%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBackground%3A%20Wasilefski%20is%20a%20longtime%20Paramount%20executive%20stepping%20in%20for%20Paul%20Mahood%2C%20the%20ad%20sales%20product%20and%20tech%20SVP%20who's%20leaving%20the%20company%20at%20the%20end%20of%20July%20after%20more%20than%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDescription%3A%20%26quot%3BOwns%20the%20significant%20vendor%20solutions%20that%20run%20our%20customer%20and%20linear%20businesses%2C%20including%20our%20CRM%20and%20all%20Salesforce%20instances%2C%20linear%20systems%2C%20and%20the%20technology%20behind%20local%2C%20sports%2C%20and%20our%20other%20non-streaming%20businesses.%20We%20will%20continue%20to%20deliver%20these%20with%20the%20availability%20and%20continuity%20the%20business%20depends%20on.%20This%20team%20owns%20the%20how%20and%20the%20when%20for%20customizing%20and%20operating%20those%20solutions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d68fab35-da09-494a-aac1-64abab3037f2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EField%20CTO%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELed%20by%20%3Cstrong%3ETravis%20Scoles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20EVP%2C%20Field%20CTO%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDescription%3A%20%26quot%3BA%20small%2C%20senior%2C%20client-facing%20team%20focused%20on%20direct%20relationships%20with%20our%20ad%20sales%20teams%20and%20advertisers.%20This%20team%20will%20build%20small%2C%20high-value%20custom%20solutions%2C%20representing%20our%20product%20and%20technology%20strategy%20to%20clients%20and%20partners%2C%20and%20feeding%20market%20intelligence%20back%20into%20the%20organization.%20Their%20work%20is%20deliberately%20one-off%3A%20anything%20that%20becomes%20durable%20is%20handed%20back%20to%20the%20broader%20organization%20to%20own%20and%20prioritize.%20The%20team%20will%20also%20represent%20Ads%20Product%20and%20Tech%20in%20client%20forums%20and%20evangelize%20Paramount%20as%20leaders%20in%20the%20Ads%20space.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22106c628f-f9eb-4607-a23e-8a632147bda1%5C%22%3EParamount%20has%20a%20new-look%20leadership%20team%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEllison's%20Paramount%20has%20had%20plenty%20of%20leadership%20changes%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20bringing%20on%20Williams%2C%20the%20company%20also%20landed%20former%20Google%20AI%20language%20product%20exec%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-hires-former-google-exec-consumer-ai-memo-david-ellison-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBarak%20Turovsky%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20May%20as%20its%20head%20of%20consumer%20AI.%20And%20in%20March%2C%20Paramount%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-hires-to-jump-start-its-ads-business-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehired%20Danielle%20Carney%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Amazon%20to%20oversee%20its%20US%20ad%20sales%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-skydance-tech-chief-leaving-read-the-memo-david-ellison-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etech%20chief%20Phil%20Wiser%3C%2Fa%3E%20left%20the%20company%20in%20late%20May.%20A%20few%20months%20earlier%2C%20agency%20partnerships%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flongtime-paramount-ad-exec-leaves-team-shakeup-david-ellison-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEVP%20Chris%20Simon%20stepped%20down%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20strea