e%20enjoyable.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELeung%20manages%20Detoorp's%20operations%2C%20optimizes%20for%20Google%20traffic%2C%20and%20plans%20to%20expand%20product%20lines.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Danny%20Leung%2C%20an%20interior%20designer%20and%20the%20founder%20of%20Detoorp%2C%20based%20in%20London%2C%20United%20Kingdom.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20work%20full%20time%20as%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-rich-people-never-have-in-homes-luxury-interior-designer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einterior%20designer%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20UK%20architecture%20practice%2C%20and%20I've%20been%20in%20the%20industry%20for%20about%2010%20years.%20I'm%20a%20creative%20person%2C%20but%20I%20found%20myself%20%26quot%3Brepeating%20life%26quot%3B%20a%20bit.%20I%20start%20a%20project%2C%20design%20it%2C%20coordinate%20with%20clients%2C%20go%20on-site%20to%20complete%20it%2C%20and%20then%20do%20it%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20like%20I%20needed%20a%20change%20of%20scenery.%20I%20wanted%20a%20side%20hustle%20that%20was%20a%20little%20bit%20different%20without%20starting%20over%20entirely.%20I%20primarily%20wanted%20something%20that%20could%20give%20me%20more%20autonomy%20in%20my%20career%20and%20allow%20me%20to%20expand%20my%20creativity%2C%20while%20earning%20extra%20income.%20It%20was%20also%20important%20to%20me%20that%20my%20side%20hustle%20be%20eco-friendly%20and%20have%20a%20positive%20impact%20on%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdetoorp.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDetoorp%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20online%20marketplace%20specializing%20in%20aesthetic%2C%20eco-friendly%20household%20and%20self-care%20products%2C%20in%202023%2C%20and%20at%20its%20peak%2C%20it%20generated%20%C2%A32%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20or%20about%20%242%2C650%2C%20in%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2262cefa19-64b0-4129-99c5-1a463e8f0f3e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20started%20my%20side%20hustle%20after%20seeing%20a%20gap%20in%20the%20market%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20been%20gaining%20greater%20financial%20stability%20in%20my%20corporate%20role%20and%20started%20investing%20in%20self-care%20products%20like%20hand%20soap%20that%20smelled%20great%20and%20complemented%20my%20home's%20interior%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20was%20doing%20routine%20chores%2C%20I%20also%20started%20to%20notice%20how%20depressing%20the%20cupboard%20looked%20with%20boring%2C%20artificial-smelling%20laundry%20detergent%20and%20other%20cleaning%20products.%20I%20did%20more%20research%20and%20came%20across%20small%20businesses%20that%20create%20eco-friendly%2C%20plant-based%20products%20using%20essential%20oils.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20I%20might%20start%20a%20platform%20or%20marketplace%20featuring%20a%20curated%20collection%20of%20aesthetically%20pleasing%2C%20great-smelling%20products%20that%20are%20also%20good%20for%20the%20environment%20%E2%80%94%20making%20chores%20a%20more%20enjoyable%2C%20uplifting%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20how%20Detoorp%20came%20about.%20The%20name%20is%20a%20combination%20of%20words%3A%20Detox%20your%20environment%2C%20make%20a%20detour%20from%20using%20harsh%20chemicals%2C%20and%20purify%20the%20planet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c0a2838c-929d-4dbd-919b-82f2468f00fc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFor%20the%20first%20few%20years%2C%20I%20worked%20on%20it%20for%20four%20hours%20after%20work%2C%20and%20the%20whole%20weekend%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20lost%20my%20free%20time%2C%20but%20I%20really%20enjoyed%20it.%20It's%20my%20own%20project%2C%20and%20I%20have%20100%25%20control%20over%20it.%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20do%20as%20people%20say%2C%20or%20get%20approval%20from%20my%20boss.%20I%20can%20do%20my%20own%20thing%2C%20which%20feels%20great.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can%20also%20follow%20my%20gut.%20I'm%20not%20even%20that%20concerned%20about%20the%20money%20since%20I'm%20still%20employed%20full-time%2C%20which%20I%20think%20is%20best%20for%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bf7c8b2e-3319-4474-b8f2-8282fa95b464%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20did%20everything%20myself%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20my%20background%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-design-a-logo-from-scratch-2009-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edesigned%20the%20logo%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20website.%20I%20handle%20digital%20marketing%2C%20take%20photos%2C%20post%20on%20Instagram%2C%20and%20order%20stock.%20I%20purchase%20wholesale%20products%20from%20platforms%20like%20Faire%20and%20other%20retailers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20stockpiled%20the%20initial%20inventory%20in%20my%20bedroom.%20I%20essentially%20had%20a%20mini-warehouse.%20Thank%20goodness%20it%20smelled%20good!%20My%20flatmate%20was%20quite%20supportive%20of%20me%20making%20a%20mess%20in%20the%20living%20room%2C%20folding%20cardboard%2C%20and%20printing%20postage%20labels.%20I%20shipped%20all%20the%20orders%20myself%20at%20the%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224261e5fb-80b2-46be-a3a2-ff65fddeb28b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20found%20it%20quite%20therapeutic%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20really%20need%20to%20think%20about%20anything.%20I%20saw%20the%20orders%2C%20packed%20them%20up%2C%20and%20then%20went%20to%20the%20post%20office%20to%20send%20them.%20It's%20a%20really%20fun%20job%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20any%20business%2C%20sales%20fluctuate%20month%20to%20month.%20The%20first%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20I%20ran%20Google%20ads.%20They%20did%20help%20bring%20people%20to%20the%20site%20to%20make%20a%20purchase%2C%20but%20they%20were%20very%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20highest%20sales%20during%20that%20time%20were%20%C2%A32%2C000%20a%20month%2C%20but%2045-50%25%20of%20that%20went%20to%20ads%20costs.%20The%20cost%20of%20goods%20is%20already%2040-50%25%20of%20the%20order%20value%2C%20plus%20there%20are%20other%20expenses%20like%20shipping.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20two%20years%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20pause%20the%20ads.%20Seeing%20those%20bills%20coming%20in%20was%20starting%20to%20wear%20on%20my%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f3c884bc-40ef-46c0-9dcd-62125788aee3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20now%20rely%20on%20organic%20traffic%20from%20Google%20and%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20use%20ChatGPT%20to%20search%20for%20product%20recommendations%2C%20and%20Deetorp%20comes%20up%20organically.%20I'm%20optimizing%20the%20website%20to%20increase%20the%20chances%20of%20showing%20up%20in%20those%20search%20results.%20I%20have%20about%2050%25%20returning%20customers%2C%20with%20a%20subset%20of%20those%20subscribing%20to%20the%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20stopped%20the%20ads%2C%20I%20started%20making%20around%20%C2%A3500-%C2%A3800%2C%20or%20around%20%24660-%20%241%2C000%2C%20in%20sales%20a%20month%2C%20with%20%C2%A3100-%20%C2%A3200%2C%20or%20around%20%24130-%20%24260%2C%20in%20profit%20a%20month.%20I'm%20really%20happy%20with%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20start%20ads%20again%20when%20the%20business%20has%20higher%20organic%20traffic%20and%20sales.%20It%20might%20be%20the%20wrong%20business%20strategy%2C%20but%20running%20ads%20was%20painful%20and%20stressful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d7416119-d078-429f-b0df-d432436e718e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20only%20spend%20around%206-10%20hours%20working%20on%20the%20business%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20I%20don't%20work%20on%20it%20at%20all.%20There%20isn't%20a%20lot%20I%20need%20to%20do%20besides%20maintain%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20pack%20the%20orders%20myself%20anymore.%20I%20send%20all%20the%20stock%20to%20a%20company%20with%20a%20warehouse%2C%20and%20its%20team%20fulfills%20all%20the%20orders.%20I%20can%20batch%20my%20social%20media%20posts%20and%20sometimes%20be%20off%20for%20a%20week%20or%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20now%20also%20have%20three%20of%20our%20own-label%20dishwashing%20products.%20I%20plan%20to%20expand%20our%20catalog%20in%20the%20near%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222cc03ffd-835a-4910-af8d-1df2eac0b7f6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20of%20the%20best%2C%20unexpected%20things%20is%20connecting%20with%20the%20customers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESometimes%20there's%20an%20issue%20with%20delivery%2C%20and%20I%20try%20to%20keep%20the%20conversation%20more%20personal%2C%20then%20offer%20a%20solution%20or%20discounts%20for%20their%20next%20purchase.%20People%20have%20been%20so%20appreciative%20and%20understanding%20that%20this%20is%20a%20small%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20really%20enjoy%20the%20process%20and%20the%20state%20of%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftested-out-side-hustles-there-are-3-i-still-use-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eside%20hustle%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Turning%20it%20into%20a%20full%20time%20business%20is%20my%20long-term%20goal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-interior-designer-started-eco-friendly-product-side-hustle-2026-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782983101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a42a9bba25092c74cca0f56%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-interior-designer-started-eco-friendly-product-side-hustle-2026-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20interior%20designer%20launched%20an%20eco-friendly%20online%20marketplace%20for%20household%20products%20to%20expand%20his%20creativity%20and%20make%20more%20money.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Suzanne%20Reilley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%2C%20Japan%20sign%20pacts%20on%20AI%2C