adult%2C%20I%20rarely%20visit%20the%20chain%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0in%20part%20because%20the%20nearest%20location%20is%20more%20than%2020%20minutes%20away%2C%20but%20I've%20also%20since%20found%20it's%20not%20as%20craveable%20as%20it%20once%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20three%20semiquincentennial%20offerings%20this%20summer%2C%20each%20priced%20at%20around%20%243.39%20in%20my%20market%2C%20though%20they're%20as%20low%20as%20%242.50%20in%20others%2C%20I%20hoped%20the%20chain%20would%20make%20a%20comeback%20in%20my%20mind.%20I%20left%20disappointed%2C%20as%20it%20was%20the%20least%20favorite%20of%20my%20four%20stops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20seasonal%2C%20USA-themed%20doughnuts%20from%20Krispy%20Kreme%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3b2dfb6891755ad48b846e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20the%20three%20doughnuts%20tasted%20exactly%20the%20same%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0plain%20rings%20with%20vanilla%20icing.%20One%20merely%20had%20sprinkles%20while%20the%20other%20had%20no%20additional%20toppings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-stuf-oreos-taste-test-review-2019-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecookies-and-cream%20filling%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20I%20found%20cloyingly%20sweet%2C%20with%20no%20discernible%20cookie%20flavor%20to%20set%20it%20apart%20from%20the%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20three%2C%20as%20part%20of%20their%20USA-themed%20decorations%2C%20featured%20highly%20concentrated%20food%20dye%20that%20stained%20my%20fingers%20and%20the%20corners%20of%20my%20mouth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20get%20me%20wrong%2C%20they%20were%20doughnuts%2C%20and%20by%20no%20means%20unpleasant%2C%20but%20unfortunately%2C%20Krispy%20Kreme's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpatriotic-cupcakes-made-in-philadelphia-2016-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epatriotic%20treats%3C%2Fa%3E%20looked%20more%20festive%20than%20they%20tasted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBurger%20King's%20cinnamon%20apple%20pie%20and%20firecracker%20cookie%20pie%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Burger%20King%20cinnamon%20apple%20pie%20and%20firecracker%20cookie%20pie%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3b2dfb3d84808d83754c85%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-burger-king-changing-whopper-recipe-premiumization-fast-food-value-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBurger%20King%3C%2Fa%3E's%20July%204th%20dessert%20menu%20includes%20its%20firecracker%20cookie%20pie%20as%20well%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bcinnamon%20apple%20pie%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20direct%20competitor%20to%20its%20longtime%20fast-food%20rival%2C%20McDonald's%20apple%20pie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cookie%20pie%20was%20explicitly%20rolled%20out%20for%20America's%20250th%20celebration%20and%20featured%20more%20festive%20packaging%20and%20decorations%2C%20while%20the%20cinnamon%20apple%20pie%20debuted%20earlier%20this%20year%20and%20will%20remain%20available%20while%20supplies%20last.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20spoonful%20of%20a%20Burger%20King%20firecracker%20cookie%20pie%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3b2dfb6891755ad48b846c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20the%20firecracker%20cookie%20pie%2C%20with%20a%20sugar-cookie%20crust%2C%20vanilla%20mousse%20filling%2C%20and%20a%20whipped%20cream%20topping%2C%20was%20a%20bit%20one-note%20and%20overly%20sweet%2C%20though%20the%20mousse%20had%20a%20pleasant%20texture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20wasn't%20to%20my%20taste%2C%20served%20cold%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20a%20refreshing%2C%20creamy%20dessert%20to%20be%20enjoyed%20on%20a%20hot%20summer%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20price%20tag%20between%20%242.99%20and%20%243.59%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20location%2C%20it%20was%20slightly%20pricier%20than%20the%20apple%20pie%2C%20but%20I%20found%20the%20cookie%20crumbs%20and%20sprinkles%20on%20top%20were%20an%20added%20patriotic%20bonus%20that%20helped%20it%20stand%20out%20from%20the%20other%20desserts%20on%20the%20list%20without%20being%20too%20try-hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Burger%20King%20cinnamon%20apple%20pie%20with%20a%20bite%20taken%20out%20of%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3b2dfbace32b985cf895d0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBurger%20King%20has%20offered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffast-food-chains-apple-pie-ranked%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehandheld%20apple%20pie%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20%E2%80%94%20notably%2C%20it%20discontinued%20its%20Dutch%20Apple%20Pie%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202020%20after%20its%20manufacturer%20stopped%20producing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20McDonald's%20vastly%20outperforms%20Burger%20King%20in%20both%20total%20revenue%20and%20average%20store%20sales%2C%20and%20the%20pie%20seemed%20a%20perfect%20example%20of%20the%20competition%3A%20Burger%20King's%20version%2C%20while%20tasty%2C%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20trying%20to%20replicate%20the%20McDonald's%20classic%20rather%20than%20carve%20out%20its%20own%20lane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20taste%20was%20very%20similar%20to%20McDonald's%20pie%2C%20the%20dough%20in%20Burger%20King's%20apple%20pie%20was%20denser%2C%20less%20flaky%2C%20and%20a%20little%20less%20flavorful%3B%20it%20also%20had%20larger%20bites%20of%20apple%20but%20a%20similar%20cinnamon%20taste%20in%20the%20filling.%20Priced%20at%20%242.13%2C%20with%20a%20range%20between%20%241.99%20and%20%242.69%20depending%20on%20location%2C%20Burger%20King's%20version%20was%20less%20expensive%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20feel%20like%20a%20better%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWienerschnitzel's%20funnel%20cake%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20apple%20pie%20funnel%20cake%20from%20Wienerschnitzel.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3b2df93d84808d83754c82%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20most%20surprising%20stop%20was%20at%20Wienerschnitzel%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0a%20brand%20that%20has%20been%20around%20since%20the%201960s%2C%20boasting%20a%20menu%20of%20%26quot%3BMmm-Merican%26quot%3B%20food%2C%20but%20one%20I%20must%20admit%20I%20am%20not%20particularly%20familiar%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20new%20menu%20item%20for%20the%20nation's%20250th%20birthday%20includes%20a%20limited-time%20summer%20menu%20of%20hot%20dogs%2C%20corn%20dogs%2C%20and%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20funnel%20cakes%20topped%20with%20apple%20pie%20filling%2C%20strawberry%2C%20or%20Oreo%20cookies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20opted%20for%20the%20apple%20%E2%80%94%20since%20what's%20more%20American%20than%20apple%20pie%3F%20%E2%80%94%20and%20found%20myself%20going%20back%20for%20bite%20after%20bite%20of%20the%20treat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20forkful%20of%20an%20apple%20pie%20funnel%20cake%20from%20Wienerschnitzel.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3b2dfa3d84808d83754c84%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20funnel%20cake%20itself%20was%20well-fried%2C%20with%20crispy%20edges%20and%20a%20fluffy%20center%2C%20and%20the%20topping%20was%20the%20classic%20mix%20of%20sweet%20and%20cinnamon%20that%20you'd%20expect.%20It%20came%20with%20a%20layer%20of%20whipped%20cream%20topping%20that%20melted%20into%20the%20cake%20since%20it%20had%20clearly%20come%20straight%20out%20of%20the%20fryer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20%246.45%20after%20tax%2C%20this%20dessert%20was%20the%20most%20expensive%20that%20I%20tried%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20they%20can%20run%20as%20much%20as%20%248.00%20depending%20on%20flavor%20and%20location%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20was%20also%20the%20biggest%2C%20and%20could%20easily%20be%20split%20between%20two%20people%20and%20still%20be%20satisfying.%20It%20was%20also%20one%20of%20my%20favorites%2C%20and%20made%20me%20want%20to%20try%20more%20of%20Wienerschnitzel's%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMcDonald's%20fried%20apple%20pie%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20packaging%20of%20McDonald's%20fried%20apple%20pie%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3b2dfa3d84808d83754c83%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20seen%20nationwide%20in%201992%2C%20McDonald's%20fried%20apple%20pies'%20return%20this%20season%20made%20headlines%20for%20good%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20golden-arched%20giant%20switched%20to%20baking%20their%20apple%20pies%2C%20fans%20lost%20the%20blistered%2C%20crispy%20crust%20you%20can%20only%20get%20from%20deep%20frying.%20Reviving%20the%20fried%20version%20in%20time%20for%20the%20nation's%20birthday%20was%20a%20deliberate%20(and%2C%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%20wildly%20successful)%20nod%20to%20McDonald's%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20America's%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20say%20this%20as%20someone%20too%20young%20to%20have%20tasted%20the%20original%20and%20therefore%20not%20biased%20by%20OG%20nostalgia%3A%20this%20thing%20slaps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20McDonald's%20fried%20apple%20pie%20with%20a%20bite%20taken%20out%20of%20it%2C%20showing%20the%20filling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a3b2dfa6891755ad48b846b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20return%20of%20its%20fried%20apple%20pie%2C%20McDonald's%20once%20again%20proved%20why%20it%20remains%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyour-favorite-restaurant-is-becoming-a-tech-company-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efast-food%20leaderboard%3C%2Fa%3E.%20At%20%243.01%2C%20the%20pie%20was%20almost%20the%20least%20expensive%20treat%20I%20tried%2C%20but%20I%20would%20have%20happily%20paid%20a%20dollar%20more%20for%20how%20much%20I%20enjoyed%20it.%20If%20you're%20lucky%2C%20you%20can%20snag%20one%20in%20a%20lower-price%20market%20for%20as%20little%20as%20%241.99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crust%20is%20delightfully%20light%20and%20flaky%2C%20a%20step%20up%20from%20the%20baked%20version%2C%20while%20the%20filling%20delivers%20the%20iconic%20apple%20flavor%20you've%20come%20to%20know%20and%20love%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-dirty-soda-refreshers-starbucks-dunkin-new-drinks-review-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eburger%20chain%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EServed%20piping%20hot%2C%20it%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20burn%20risk%2C%20but%20what's%20the%204th%20of%20July%20without%20a%20little%20fire%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20h