ssinsider.com%2Findex%2Fkospi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKospi%20index%3C%2Fa%3E%20ended%207.9%25%20lower%2C%20with%20heavyweights%20SK%20Hynix%20and%20Samsung%20Electronics%20tanking%2014.6%25%20and%209.1%25%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chip%20selloff%20spilled%20into%20Japan%2C%20where%20chipmaker%20Kioxia%20%E2%80%94%20the%20country's%20most%20valuable%20company%20%E2%80%94%20tumbled%20more%20than%2013.5%25%2C%20dragging%20the%20Nikkei%20225%20down%202.5%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProfit-taking%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20key%20driver%2C%26quot%3B%20Fabien%20Yip%2C%20a%20market%20analyst%20at%20IG%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20note.%20She%20pointed%20out%20that%20even%20after%20Thursday's%20declines%2C%20SK%20Hynix%20remains%20up%20more%20than%20200%25%20this%20year%2C%20while%20Kioxia%20has%20surged%20over%20500%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korea%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20best-performing%20stock%20markets%20this%20year%2C%20fueled%20by%20a%20surge%20in%20semiconductor%20and%20AI-related%20shares.%20The%20strong%20rally%20has%20left%20the%20market%20more%20susceptible%20to%20sharp%20pullbacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThursday's%20selloff%20extended%20a%20volatile%20run%20in%20South%20Korea's%20Kospi%2C%20fueled%20by%20heavy%20selling%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkorean-chipmaker-stock-selloff-samsung-sk-hynix-global-market-weakness-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleveraged%20ETFs%3C%2Fa%3E%20tracking%20Samsung%20and%20SK%20Hynix.%20The%20swings%20have%20triggered%20multiple%20trading%20halts%20over%20the%20past%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20are%20also%20concerned%20about%20Samsung%20and%20SK%20Hynix's%20%24520%20billion%20investment%20into%20four%20new%20memory%20chip%20plants%20in%20South%20Korea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20can%20happen%20to%20a%20technology%20cycle%20in%20that%20window%2C%20and%20AI%20infrastructure%20spending%20may%20potentially%20slow%20once%20the%20current%20