2-units-in-june-exports-jump-47-126070200196_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fauto%2Fbajaj-auto-total-sales-up-28-to-463-202-units-in-june-exports-jump-47-126070200196_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fauto%2Fbajaj-auto-total-sales-up-28-to-463-202-units-in-june-exports-jump-47-126070200196_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Base44's%20CEO%20says%20the%20company%20built%20its%20own%20model%20to%20stop%20churning%20out%20AI-slop%20designs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Base44's%20CEO%20Maor%20Shlomo%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a44a0afa25092c74cca1d3d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221005%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBase44's%20CEO%20said%20the%20company%20developed%20its%20own%20AI%20model%20to%20deliver%20what%20frontier%20models%20can't.%3Cp%3EBase44%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBase44%20wants%20to%20make%20sure%20your%20next%20vibe-coded%20website%20doesn't%20look%20like%20AI%20slop.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20startup%20launched%20its%20LLM%2C%20Base%201%2C%20to%20deliver%20better%20designs%20and%20user%20experience%20than%20frontier%20models.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECEO%20Maor%20Shlomo%20said%20he%20hopes%20Base%201%20will%20deliver%20unique%20designs%20each%20time%2C%20although%20it's%20not%20there%20yet.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBase44%20wants%20to%20help%20users%20ditch%20the%20cookie-cutter%20look%20of%20AI-coded%20websites%20with%20its%20new%20AI%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbase44-vibecoding-tools-easy-to-copy-maor-shlomo-risk-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESan%20Francisco-based%20vibe%20coding%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E%20announced%20on%20Monday%20that%20it%20had%20trained%20and%20released%20its%20own%20large%20language%20model%20called%20Base%201.%20Before%20giving%20the%20prompt%20to%20the%20platform%20to%20build%20an%20app%2C%20users%20can%20now%20select%20Base%201%20from%20a%20selection%20of%20AI%20models%2C%20including%20Claude's%20Opus%204.8%2C%20Fable%205%2C%20and%20OpenAI's%20GPT-5.5.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShlomo%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20his%20company%20developed%20its%20own%20model%20was%20to%20combat%20the%20telltale%20generic%20look%20that%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeginners-guide-ai-vibe-coding-lovable-base44-claude-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evibe-coded%20products%20have%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20problem%20with%20using%20frontier%20models%20for%20making%20websites%20is%20that%20%26quot%3Beverybody%20feels%20like%20they're%20getting%20the%20same%20UI%20when%20they're%20coding%20with%20the%20general%20models.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBase44%20was%20acquired%20by%20Wix%20last%20June%20for%20%2480%20million%2C%20making%20it%20part%20of%20Wix's%20website-building%20arsenal.%20Shlomo%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvibe-coding-website-lovable-wix-ai-writing-portfolio-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esaid%20Wix%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20a%20large%20team%20of%20designers%2C%20which%20generates%20a%20lot%20of%20data%20for%20its%20model%20to%20train%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Base44%20team%20will%20conduct%20%26quot%3Breinforcement%20learning%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20new%20model%2C%20Shlomo%20said%2C%20which%20involves%20prompting%20it%20to%20keep%20generating%20designs%20that%20look%20new%20and%20unique.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Base%201%20is%20%26quot%3Bnot%20yet%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Shlomo%20said%20he%20aims%20for%20it%20to%20%26quot%3Bcreate%20something%20that%20looks%20uniquely%20different%26quot%3B%20each%20time%20it%20generates%20a%20user%20interface.%20He%20said%20the%20team%20started%20working%20on%20Base%201%20about%20six%20months%20ago%2C%20but%20had%20breakthroughs%20in%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20release%20the%20model%20sooner%20than%20planned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20generating%20unique%20designs%20will%20set%20Base44%20apart%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmake-app-cursor-lovable-base44-vibe-coding-tools-comparison-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efrom%20competitors%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Startups%20like%20Lovable%2C%20Replit%2C%20and%20Cursor%20compete%20with%20Base44.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20UI%2FUX%20experts%20and%20design%20gurus%20have%20warned%20about%20the%20AI%20slop%20look%20on%20vibe-coded%20websites%20and%20apps.%20Paul%20Bakaus%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20AI%20design%20startup%20Impeccable%2C%20said%20in%20a%20June%20interview%20with%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%20that%20telltale%20signs%20of%20AI-coded%20products%20include%20beige%20or%20tinted%20backgrounds%20and%20sans-serif%20fonts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBakaus%20likened%20it%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Balgorithmic%20Uniqlo%20or%20Ikea%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20design%20that's%20not%20bad%2C%20but%20not%20unique.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShlomo%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20frontier%20models%20must%20be%20generically%20good%20at%20everything%2C%20from%20poetry%20to%20coding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20think%20that%20if%20we%20take%20a%20model%20and%20we%20squeeze%20its%20ability%20to%20be%20really%2C%20really%20good%20at%20one%20use%20case%2C%20then%20we%20have%20a%20shot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbase44-ceo-maor-shlomo-built-llm-combat-ai-slop-design-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782967724000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a45c027ec11c5f7e7fa76e6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbase44-ceo-maor-shlomo-built-llm-combat-ai-slop-design-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20startup%20launched%20its%20LLM%2C%20Base%201%2C%20to%20deliver%20better%20designs%20and%20user%20experience%20than%20frontier%20models.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abharade%40insider.com%20(Aditi%20Bharade)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A97%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22WhatsApp%20usernames%20decoded%3A%20Your%20questions%20answered%2C%20government's%20concerns%20explained%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782967649000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132129163%2Cimgsize-74963.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fwhatsapp-usernames-decoded-your-questions-answered-governments-concerns-explained%2Farticleshow%2F132129127.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20government%20has%20urged%20Meta%20to%20halt%20WhatsApp%20usernames%2C%20citing%20concerns%20over%20potential%20impersonation%20and%20cybercrime.%20While%20Meta%20claims%20usernames%20enhance%20privacy%20by%20obscuring%20phone%20numbers%2C%20officials%20fear%20it%20could%20aid%20bad%20actors.%20The%20feature%20allows%20users%20to%20create%20unique%20handles%2C%20but%20the%20government%20seeks%20assurances%20on%20its%20security%20before%20widespread%20adoption.%20This%20move%20could%20significantly%20impact%20how%20users%20interact%20and%20protect%20their%20digital%20identities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22AABHAS%20SHARMA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia's%20disrupted%20supply%20routes%20are%20forcing%20its%20troops%20to%20walk%2018%20miles%20to%20the%20front%2C%20Fedorov%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225077%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Russian%20soldiers%20holding%20rifles%20shout.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a45d869ec11c5f7e7fa771a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222964%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20military%20servicemen%20shout%20during%20the%20Victory%20Day%202026%20parade%20in%20Moscow.%3Cp%3EContributor%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUkraine's%20defense%20minister%20said%20Russian%20troops%20are%20now%20walking%2018%20miles%20to%20the%20front%20lines.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat%20takes%20a%20soldier%20with%20combat%20gear%20about%20six%20to%20eight%20hours.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20come%20as%20Ukraine%20has%20tried%20to%20disrupt%20the%20Kremlin's%20supply%20lines%20in%20the%20southern%20rear.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20crippled%20logistics%20routes%20on%20the%20war's%20southern%20front%20are%20forcing%20its%20infantry%20to%20walk%20some%2018%20miles%20to%20their%20combat%20positions%2C%20Ukraine's%20defense%20minister%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou've%20already%20seen%2C%20for%20example%2C%20in%20the%20south%2C%20where%20Russian%20infantry%2C%20due%20to%20logistics%20being%20disrupted%2C%20are%20walking%2030%20kilometers%20on%20foot%20to%20reach%20positions%2C%26quot%3B%20Mykhailo%20Fedorov%20said%20at%20a%20joint%20press%20conference%20in%20Kyiv%20with%20his%20Swedish%20counterpart%2C%20P%C3%A5l%20Jonson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussian%20and%20Ukrainian%20troops%20are%20typically%20moved%20by%20vehicle%20to%20intermediate%20positions%20before%20traveling%20the%20last%20few%20miles%20on%20foot%2C%20at%20night%2C%20or%20in%20smaller%20vehicles%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-drone-kill-zone-is-getting-bigger-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eavoid%20detection%20by%20light%20drones.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarching%2030%20km%2C%20or%20about%2018%20miles%2C%20in%20one%20go%20would%20take%20a%20soldier%20in%20combat%20gear%20at%20least%20six%20to%20eight%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFedorov%20said%20Russian%20forces%20have%20had%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20problems%20getting%20infantry%20to%20the%20front%20line%26quot%3B%20and%20sending%20them%20supplies%2C%20fuel%2C%20and%20generators%20used%20by%20drone%20operators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20logistics%20disruption%20comes%20as%20Ukraine%20has%20increasingly%20used%20a%20newer%20class%20of%20drone%20capable%20of%20striking%20at%20depths%20of%2030%20to%20300%20km%2C%20targeting%20Russian%20supply%20routes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-mid-range-drone-crimea-bridge-slam-asphalt-strike-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebombing%20trucks%2C%20bridges%2C%20and%20facilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20rear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20problems%20not%20obvious%20at%20first%20glance%20that%20affect%20the%20intensity%20of%20enemy%20actions%20on%20our%20territory%2C%26quot%3B%20Fedorov%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrimea%2C%20a%20major%20logistics%20hub%20for%20Russian%20operations%20in%20Kherson%20and%20Zaporizhzhia%2C%20is%20also%20facing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-squeeze-crimea-fuel-cut-mid-range-drones-sevastopol-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esevere%20energy%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20Ukrainian%20mid-range%20drones%20bombard%20oil%20facilities%20and%20key%20bridges%20connecting%20the%20peninsula%20to%20the%20mainland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocal%20officials%20began%20rationing%20fuel%20for%20civilians%20last%20month%20before%20announcing%20they%20would%20cut%20fuel%20sales%20indefinitely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20large%20number%20of%20crises%20are%20beginning%20to%20accumulate%2C%20and%20it%20is%20becoming%20increasingly%20difficult%20for%20Russians%20to%20resolve%20crisis%20after%20crisis%2C%26quot%3B%20Fedorov%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mid-range%20drone%20has%20been%20key%20to%20Ukraine's%20renewed%20war%20effort%2C%20giving%20Kyiv%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-himars-mid-range-drones-strike-atacms-russia-analysts-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eintermediate-range%20strike%20capacity%3C%2Fa%3