%20baseball%20cap%20and%20sports%20jacket%20with%20baby-pink%20pants%20and%20shoes%20%E2%80%94%20when%20he%20rang%20the%20Opening%20Bell%20for%20Eightco%20Holdings%20Inc%20(ticker%3A%20%24ORBS)%20at%20the%20Nasdaq%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20chaired%20the%20company's%20board%20until%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20August%2C%20Ives%20launched%20a%20clothing%20brand%20reflecting%20his%20unique%20style%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Brooklyn-based%20upcycled%20streetwear%20label%20Snow%20Milk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2290aed249-aa65-41c0-a8d2-b63cbbeab469%5C%22%3E5.%20Jacket-on-hoodie%20looks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dan%20Ives%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a45d632ec11c5f7e7fa7711%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223814%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIves%20almost%20always%20matches%20his%20jackets%20to%20his%20sneakers.%3Cp%3E%24ORBS)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20another%20Orbs%20event%20in%20October%2C%20the%20tech%20bull%20wore%20a%20neon%20printed%20blazer%20under%20a%20colorful%20green%20hoodie.%20In%20his%20signature%20style%2C%20he%20paired%20it%20with%20multicolored%20sneakers%20that%20almost%20exactly%20matched%20his%20jacket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20wore%20it%20with%20a%20printed%20baseball%20cap%20and%20sunglasses.%20Yes%2C%20the%20event%20was%20indoors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20definitely%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20global%20success%2C%20because%20of%20the%20way%20that%20I%20dress%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20September.%20%26quot%3BEven%20people%20who%20don't%20know%20my%20stock%20calls%2C%20they%20know%20me%20as%20the%20person%20who%20wears%20the%20funky%20shirts%20on%20CNBC.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdan-ives-wedbush-tech-calls-outfits-nvidia-microsoft-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fd