%202025%20in%20an%20article%20about%20how%20eggs%20are%20probably%20just%20going%20to%20be%20expensive%E2%80%A6%20forever.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EShe%20talked%20to%20a%20ton%20of%20people%20well%20placed%20to%20know%20what%20was%20driving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fegg-prices-expensive-avian-bird-flu-changing-tastes-cage-free-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20cost%20of%20eggs%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20egg%20industry%20experts%20(there's%20someone%20with%20the%20amazing%20job%20title%20%26quot%3Bmanaging%20editor%20of%20eggs%20in%20the%20Americas%26quot%3B)%2C%20professors%20of%20veterinary%20medicine%2C%20epidemiologists%2C%20and%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20American%20Egg%20Board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experts%20agreed%20that%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20factors%20like%20certain%20state%20laws%20on%20farming%20practices%20(a%20few%20states%20have%20cage-free%20laws%20that%20make%20local%20egg%20production%20more%20expensive)%2C%20the%20biggest%20factor%20was%20the%20spread%20of%20avian%20flu%2C%20which%20was%20more%20widespread%20than%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20no%20one%20seemed%20to%20know%20at%20the%20time%20was%20that%20there%20was%20perhaps%20another%20factor%20going%20on%3A%20price%20fixing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223b145e8c-42f4-46c5-b452-a9bf695ae9bd%5C%22%3EThe%20egg%20price-fixing%20scandal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fopa%2Fpr%2Fjustice-department-requires-egg-producers-end-coordinated-benchmark-manipulation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDepartment%20of%20Justice%20just%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week%20that%20it%20has%20proposed%20a%20settlement%20for%20an%20investigation%20against%20three%20big%20egg%20producers%2C%20alleging%20that%20between%202022%20and%20March%202025%2C%20they%20colluded%20to%20keep%20prices%20high%20by%20coordinating%20bids%20on%20egg%20exchanges%2C%20or%20the%20market%20where%20egg%20producers%20buy%20and%20sell%20from%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20egg%20producers%2C%20Cal-Maine%2C%20Versova%2C%20and%20Hickman's%20Egg%20Ranch%2C%20allegedly%20spoke%20on%20the%20phone%20and%20over%20text%20to%20make%20plans%20about%20how%20to%20keep%20prices%20high%2C%20which%20ultimately%20would%20affect%20what%20you%20saw%20in%20the%20grocery%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20settlement%20by%20the%20DOJ%2C%20along%20with%2017%20state%20attorneys%20general%2C%20requires%20the%20three%20egg%20companies%20to%20pay%20a%20combined%20%243.3%20million%20fine%20and%20donate%20over%2050%20million%20eggs%20to%20food%20banks.%20The%20settlement%20has%20to%20be%20accepted%20by%20a%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20companies%20have%20agreed%20to%20the%20settlement%2C%20which%20doesn't%20require%20admission%20of%20any%20wrongdoing.%20In%20a%20statement%2C%20a%20representative%20for%20Versova%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20decision%20to%20accept%20this%20settlement%20simply%20reflects%20our%20firm%20intention%20to%20put%20this%20matter%20behind%20us%20and%20focus%20on%20our%20business.%26quot%3B%20A%20representative%20for%20MTQ%20USA%2C%20Hickman's%20owner%2C%20said%20that%20the%20issue%20predates%20its%20acquisition%20of%20the%20company%20in%20November%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20to%20say%20that%20manipulation%20was%20the%20main%20or%20only%20factor.%20The%20avian%20flu%20epidemic%20was%20real%20and%20affected%20lots%20of%20producers.%20Hickman's%2C%20for%20example%2C%20said%20in%20June%202025%20that%20the%20flu%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20deaths%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kjzz.org%2Fbusiness%2F2025-05-31%2Fhickmans-just-lost-95-of-arizona-chickens-to-bird-flu-and-says-it-will-take-2-years-to-rebuild%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E95%25%20of%20its%20flock%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f592bb57-b968-42bd-ac1a-1fdff8311c59%5C%22%3EEgg%20prices%20got%20political%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20feels%2C%20to%20me%2C%20so%20infuriating%20about%20this%20(alleged)%20price-fixing%20is%20how%20huge%20a%20deal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feggs-expensive-high-prices-supply-shortage-bird-flu-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eegg%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20at%20the%20time.%20We%20couldn't%20stop%20talking%20about%20egg%20prices!%20It%20was%20constantly%20in%20the%20news.%20(I%20admit%20some%20bias%20here%2C%20as%20someone%20involved%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feggs-prices-shortage-avian-bird-flu-eggshells-grocery-store-why-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewriting%20about%20egg%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20this%20period.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEggs%20became%20the%20avatar%20of%20the%20entire%20cost%20of%20groceries%20and%20the%20overall%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-january-cpi-consumer-price-index-federal-reserve-interest-rates-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecost-of-living%20crunch%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20average%20Americans.%20Inflation%20during%20the%202020s%20made%20nearly%20everything%20more%20expensive%2C%20and%20rising%20grocery%20prices%20hurt%20the%20pockets%20of%20millions%20of%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FCmrER%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Line%20chart%20of%20the%20average%20price%20of%20a%20dozen%20large%20Grade%20A%20eggs%20over%20the%20years%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FCmrER%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20incredibly%20political%2C%20too.%20During%20the%202024%20election%20cycle%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fap-votecast-trump-harris-election-president-voters-86225516e8424431ab1d19e57a74f198%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecost%20of%20groceries%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20eggs%20%E2%80%94%20was%20a%20top%20issue%20for%20candidates.%20It's%20probably%20a%20stretch%20to%20say%20egg%20prices%20clinched%20the%20election%20for%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20%3Cem%3Etotally%3C%2Fem%3E%20wrong.%20Lots%20of%20voters%20listened%20to%20his%20promises%20to%20ease%20inflation%2C%20especially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcepr.net%2Fpublications%2Fharris-defeat%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earound%20grocery%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20himself%20believed%20he%20won%20based%20on%20egg%20prices.%20In%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fdonald-trump%2Fread-transcript-president-donald-trump-interviewed-nbc-news-meet-press-rcna348508%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%20with%20%26quot%3BMeet%20the%20Press%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fa%3Ejust%20before%20he%20took%20office%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20buy%20apples%2C%20when%20you%20buy%20bacon%2C%20when%20you%20buy%20eggs%2C%20they%20would%20double%20and%20triple%20the%20price%20over%20a%20short%20period%20of%20time%2C%20and%20I%20won%20an%20election%20based%20on%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202025%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%20Emily%20Stewart%20wrote%20about%20eggs%20being%20expensive%20forever%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.bls.gov%2Ftimeseries%2FAPU0000708111%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprices%20hit%20%244.95%20a%20dozen%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sen.%20Elizabeth%20Warren%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.warren.senate.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2Fwarren-mcgovern-lawmakers-blast-trumps-inaction-on-high-egg-prices%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Especifically%20about%20egg%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20demanding%20to%20know%20when%20he'd%20fulfill%20his%20campaign%20promises%20to%20lower%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20months%20later%2C%20when%20prices%20hit%20an%20all-time%20high%20of%20%246.23%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20announced%20its%20investigation%20into%20the%20alleged%20price-fixing%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20eats%20a%20decent%20amount%20of%20eggs%2C%20it's%20indeed%20aggravating%20to%20have%20to%20pay%20more.%20It's%20extra%20infuriating%20to%20imagine%20that%20this%20isn't%20just%20because%20of%20unfortunate%20circumstances%20like%20a%20bird%20flu%20outbreak%2C%20but%20because%20of%20some%20form%20of%20illegal%20manipulation.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20mad!%20I%20mean%2C%20I%20guess%20I'm%20always%20mad%20about%20illegal%20price%20fixing%2C%20but%20this%20affected%20me%20directly%20%E2%80%94%20both%20because%20I%20had%20to%20pay%20more%20at%20the%20store%2C%20and%20also%20because%20so%20much%20of%20our%20mental%20energy%20had%20gone%20into%20talking%20about%20the%20price%20of%20eggs.%20I%20feel%20glaslit!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-egg-price-fixing-lawsuit-settlement-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782938961000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4577262680585ce91a3570%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-egg-price-fixing-lawsuit-settlement-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sky-high%20egg%20prices%2C%20supposedly%20due%20to%20the%20avian%20flu%2C%20were%20such%20a%20big%20deal%20leading%20up%20to%20the%202025%20election.%20Turns%20out%2C%20they%20may%20have%20been%20fixed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22knotopoulos%40businessinsider.com%20(Katie%20Notopoulos)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A92%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22YouTuber%20Stephen%20McCullagh%20appeals%20life%20sentence%20after%20murdering%20pregnant%20girlfriend%20and%20using%20fake%20GTA%20livestream%20alibi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1782936853000%2C%22visual%2