0attending%20regularly%20because%20of%20the%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20rule%3A%20%E2%80%98No%20School%2C%20No%20Football%E2%80%99.%20Barriers%20of%20caste%20and%20religion%20dissolved%20on%20the%20field%2C%20replaced%20by%20teamwork%2C%20discipline%2C%20and%20respect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-4-1757076545.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rathod%20aims%20to%20enrich%20children%E2%80%99s%20lives%20with%20the%20discipline%2C%20teamwork%2C%20and%20hope%20derived%20from%20football.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-4-1757076545.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-4-1757076545-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-4-1757076545-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-4-1757076545-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Ffootball-4-1757076545-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-497019%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERathod%20aims%20to%20enrich%20children%E2%80%99s%20lives%20with%20the%20discipline%2C%20teamwork%2C%20and%20hope%20derived%20from%20football.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20breakthrough%20came%20when%20the%20Education%20Department%20of%20Daman%20and%20Diu%20invited%20OSCAR%20to%20tackle%20rising%20suicides%20and%20poor%20attendance%20in%20schools.%20Ashok%E2%80%99s%20team%20trained%20154%20teachers%20in%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F493590%2Fswap-your-screen-for-